From: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Date: Fri, 8 Nov 2024 16:37:53 -0800
Subject: tools api io: Ensure line_len_out is always initialized
Git-commit: f4db95b68ae68ebaf91d35cc0487ac1cbd04261e
Patch-mainline: v6.13-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

Ensure initialization to avoid compiler warnings about potential use
of uninitialized variables.

Signed-off-by: Ian Rogers <irogers@google.com>
Cc: Ravi Bangoria <ravi.bangoria@amd.com>
Cc: Yoshihiro Furudera <fj5100bi@fujitsu.com>
